<preface id="preface" xreflabel="preface">
<title>Preface</title>


<para>
The kernel-org Roll enables users to incorporate custom-compiled kernel.org
kernels into their Rocks (TM) cluster.  This roll is intended for 
<emphasis>advanced users and administrators</emphasis> who require kernel configurations not supplied by the upstream vendor  
</para>


<warning>
<para>
Using kernels from <ulink
url="http://www.kernel.org">kernel.org
</ulink> may adversely affect stability of your cluster. This roll creates 
<computeroutput>kernel</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>kernel-headers</computeroutput> packages only. 
</para>
</warning>
</preface>
